OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly fine,
OL,6,Fwith the risk of heavy thundery
OL,7,Fshowers receding in the southeast into
OL,8,Fthe evening. Dry overnight with clear
OL,9,Fperiods, as well as low cloud making
OL,10,Finroads into southern coastal
OL,11,Fdistricts. Widely humid, very warm in
OL,12,Finland urban areas.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FMainly fine, but with low
OL,15,Fcloud in some southern and western
OL,16,Fareas, and with a humid feel
OL,17,Fgenerally. Becoming hot in developing
OL,18,Fsunny periods, perhaps triggering
OL,19,Fisolated thundery showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
