OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Flittle less hot on Saturday, but
OL,7,Fbecoming fine with heat building,
OL,8,Fperhaps peaking on Monday, with some
OL,9,Fmuggy intervening nights. This heat
OL,10,Fperhaps triggering thunderstorms by
OL,11,Fthis time.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
